"Never run in production with DEBUG enabled. Debug mode exposes internal "
"details and stack traces."
msgstr ""
"Peidiwch byth â rhedeg mewn cynhyrchiad gyda DEBUG wedi'i alluogi. Mae modd "
"dadfygio yn datgelu manylion mewnol ac olion pyst."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Always deploy Grylli behind a reverse proxy (e.g. Caddy, Nginx, or Traefik) "
"and serve it over HTTPS. Sensitive user data must be encrypted in transit."
msgstr ""
"Bob amser rhowch Grylli y tu ôl i proxy gwrthdro (e.e. Caddy, Nginx, neu "
"Traefik) a'i wasanaethu dros HTTPS. Rhaid amgryptio data defnyddiwr sensitif"
" wrth ei gludo."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:50
msgid ""
"Ensure the data folder (database) is backed up regularly. Backups are stored"
" in the 'backups' folder."
msgstr ""
"Sicrhewch fod ffeil y ffolder data (cronfa ddata) wedi'i gwneud copi wrth "
"gefn ar eich gwesteiwr"

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:53
msgid ""
"The uploads folder is shared. To isolate attachments per user, configure "
"host-level directories and access controls."
msgstr ""
"Rhennir y ffolder lanlwythiadau. I insiwlio atodiadau fesul defnyddiwr, "
"ffurfweddwch gyfeiriaduron lefel-gwesteiwr a rheolaethau mynediad."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:55
msgid ""
"To restore a backup: stop the container, replace the grylli.db file from a "
"backup, and restart."
msgstr ""
"I adfer copi wrth gefn: stopiwch y cynhwysydd, ailosodwch data/grylli.db "
"gyda un o'r ffolder copïau wrth gefn, a chychwyn y cynhwysydd eto."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Admins cannot remove their own admin role to prevent accidental lockout."
msgstr ""
"Ni all haciwr tir gael eu rôl admin ei hun i atal cloi allan damweiniol."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:58
msgid ""
"Rate limits and automatic account lockouts are enforced to protect against "
"brute-force login attempts."
msgstr ""
"Mae terfynau cyfradd a chloiadau cyfrif awtomatig yn gorfodi i amddiffyn yn "
"erbyn ymdrechion mewngofnodi gorfodol."

#: app/templates/admin/index.html:60
msgid ""
"Passwords, SMTP credentials, and API tokens are encrypted at rest using "
"Fernet."
msgstr ""
"Mae cyfrineiriau, cymwysterau SMTP, a thocynnau API wedi'u hamgryptio ar "
"orffwys gan ddefnyddio Fernet."

